title: Being Human (UK) - Complete Series - Updated August 2016
description:
Update August 2016:
Since KickAss Torrents is gone, I decided to recompile this release to include the correct video for Season 05, Episode 04, titled "The Greater Good".  In my previous torrent on TPB, I had the incorrect video in the collection, which was a duplicate of Season 05, Episode 03.



This is the complete series of Being Human (UK) video files I managed to acquire.

IMDB: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1349938/
